article_title: Head of Hamas aerial unit killed in strike, IDF says.
sentence: Head  of  Hamas  aerial  unit  killed  in  strike,  IDF  says.

article_title: Head of Hamas aerial unit killed in strike, IDF says.
sentence: The  Israel  Defense  Forces  (IDF)  say  a  high-ranking  member  of  Hamas,  Samer  Abu  Daqqa,  was  killed  last  month  in  a  strike  by  the  Israeli  Air  Force.
